Attribute.name: Text
Attribute.original:
<script>
$(function(){
var flag = 0;
var num = $('.helperFontSizeN');
for (var i = 0; i < num.length; i++) {
  var $currentNum = $(num[i]);
  var $cardBody = $currentNum.closest('.card__body');
  if (flag == 0) {
                          var tam = num[i].innerHTML.length;
  	  switch (true) {
    	  case (tam > 8 &&  tam < 11):
    		$cardBody.find('.helperFontSizeC, .helperFontSizeN').addClass('font20');
	  	$cardBody.find('.helperFontSizeC, .helperFontSizeN').removeClass('font27');
	        flag = 1;
                          break;
                          case (tam > 11 && tam < 14):
	                        $cardBody.find('.helperFontSizeC, .helperFontSizeN').addClass('font16');
	  	$cardBody.find('.helperFontSizeC, .helperFontSizeN').removeClass('font27');
	       flag = 1;
                          break;
   	  default:
                                                $cardBody.find('.helperFontSizeC, .helperFontSizeN').addClass('font27');
	  break;
 	  }
  } 
flag = 0;
}

})
</script>
